OL,3,CDate set for Dumfries & Galloway
OL,4,CCouncil no confidence vote
OL,6,FThe Conservative administration on
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Council will
OL,8,Fface a vote of no confidence in their
OL,9,Fleadership.
OL,11,FLeader councillor Gail MacGregor said
OL,12,Fshe would "love to continue in the
OL,13,Frole."
OL,15,FDumfries and Galloway Council have
OL,16,Fconfirmed that there will be a special
OL,17,Fmeeting of full council on Monday,
OL,18,FJune 16.
