OL,4,CCouncil no confidence vote
OL,6,FIt comes after seven Conservative
OL,7,Fcouncillors left the party, making the
OL,8,FSNP the biggest group.
OL,10,FCouncillor Gail MacGregor has been the
OL,11,Fleader of the Conservative
OL,12,Fadministration since 2023, when an SNP-
OL,13,Fled rainbow coalition collapsed.
