OL,4,CCouncil no confidence vote
OL,6,FShe said: "Under my leadership for the
OL,7,Fpast two years I've managed to steer a
OL,8,Fvery steady ship with support from
OL,9,Facross the parties and having to make
OL,10,Fsome compromises. Going forward in the
OL,11,Fnext two weeks I don't know what will
OL,12,Fhappen. I would like to assure people
OL,13,Fthat my heart is always in delivering
OL,14,Ffor the region and creating that
OL,15,Fstability. This is a chink in the road
OL,16,Fthat I didn't expect."
