OL,4,CCouncil no confidence vote
OL,6,FSNP group business manager Councillor
OL,7,FKatie Hagmann told ITV Border her
OL,8,Fparty had submitted a no confidence
OL,9,Fmotion that has received cross party
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FIn February, councillors voted through
OL,13,Fthe opposition SNP budget.
OL,15,FCouncillor Katie Hagmann said the
OL,16,Fadministration was in "disarray."
