OL,6,FShe added: "We have submitted a motion
OL,7,Fof no confidence in the current
OL,8,Fadministration. There is likely to be
OL,9,Fan announcement of a full council
OL,10,Fmeeting and we are calling for the
OL,11,Fremoval of the convener and the deputy
OL,12,Fconvener, which is also the leader of
OL,13,FDumfries and Galloway council.
OL,15,F"It is not acceptable the way that the
OL,16,Fadministration is acting and the SNP
OL,17,Fgroup are the biggest group within the
OL,18,Fwhole of the council and this is an
OL,19,Fsnp budget that's been passed.
