OL,6,F"We've got business to do, we've got
OL,7,Fto deliver for the people of Dumfries
OL,8,Fand Galloway and we're determined to
OL,9,Fdo that."
OL,11,FThe Conservative rebels have formed
OL,12,Ftwo separate groups.
OL,14,FCouncillors Andrew Giusti, Chrissie
OL,15,FHill, David Inglis and Richard Marsh
OL,16,Fhave formed a new group called
OL,17,FNovantae.
