OL,6,FThe three other councillors Ian
OL,7,FCarruthers, Karen Carruthers and
OL,8,FAndrew Wood, have formed a separate
OL,9,Findependent group.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Scottish
OL,12,FConservatives said: "We wish them
OL,13,Fwell."
OL,15,FThe rebellion means that the
OL,16,FConservative group shrinks from 16 to
OL,17,Fnine and raises questions over the
OL,18,Fviability of the current
OL,19,Fadministration.
