OL,6,FThe political make-up of the council
OL,7,Fis now: 11 SNP members; nine Scottish
OL,8,FConservatives; eight Scottish Labour;
OL,9,Fone Scottish Liberal Democrat; 14
OL,10,Findependent / other.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Dumfries and
OL,13,FGalloway Council said:
OL,15,F"Dumfries and Galloway Council can
OL,16,Fconfirm that seven councillors have
OL,17,Fresigned from the Conservative group.
OL,18,FThe council's website has been updated.
