OL,6,F"Four of the councillors have formed a
OL,7,Fnew political group called Novantae `
OL,8,Fcouncillors Richard Marsh, Chrissie
OL,9,FHill, Andrew Giusti and David Inglis.
OL,11,F"Three of the councillors have
OL,12,Finformed council officers that they
OL,13,Fhave set up a separate group and they
OL,14,Fintend to call it The Dumfries and
OL,15,FGalloway Independent Group. These are
OL,16,Fcouncillors Ian Carruthers, Karen
OL,17,FCarruthers and Andrew Wood.
OL,19,F"The council will not be commenting
OL,20,Ffurther at this time."
